Sections of the ChocAn project that will be computerized include all user and provider storage and management.
In addition to this, the terminal that operators and managers use to interact with the system will also be computerized.
The data will be stored in the ChocAn data center. Hardware that will be required is a data center, as well as computers for the ChocAn terminals.
The ChocAn system developed will interact with other ChocAn designed terminals that providers use. Users will interact with the system through the ChocAn terminals.